Sentencas: MnO-Co composite was employed to modify a Ni-Sm0.2Ce0.8O2 (-) (x) anode.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of the MnO-Co modified anode was evaluated on an anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell in dry hydrogen and dry methane, separately.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The modified anode exhibited much higher peak power density in H-2 compared with the original anode at the same condition.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For example, the peak power density by the modified anode was 1756 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C, compared with 1322 mW cm(-2) by the original anode at the same temperature.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The higher peak power density of modified anode was attributed to its much lower polarization resistance and relatively higher porosity.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, it showed a worse stability than the unmodified anode in dry methane at 650 degrees C due to severer carbon deposition.
Titulo: MnO-Co composite modified Ni-SDC anode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
